    "| Tokens      | Time steps (prices, returns)   |\n",
    "| Sentence    | Price history window           |\n",
    "| Vocabulary  | Feature space (indicators)     |\n",
    "| Sequence    | Time series                    |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Padding in Finance\n",
    "Different assets / samples have:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Different history lengths\n",
    "- Missing observations\n",
    "\n",
    "Example:\n",
    "\n",
    "- Stock A: `[r₁, r₂, r₃, r₄]`\n",
    "- Stock B: `[r₁, r₂]`\n",
    "\n",
    "Pad: `[r₁, r₂, 0, 0]`\n",
    "\n",
    "### Masking in Finance\n",
